28 October 2008Government will hold cluster media briefings on the implementation of government's Programme of Action. The briefings will take place at the Union Buildings in Pretoria, in room 153.There will be a video link-up to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town, for all briefings.Briefing schedule:Thursday, 30 October 2008 11:00 - 12:30 Justice, Crime Prevention and Security Cluster Chair: Minister Nathi MthethwaEnquiries Bongiwe Gambu (Pretoria) Cell: 076 403 9496Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)